br />\n<br />\n民間記者會傳媒邀請函<br />\n<br />\n第二次的民間記者會主題為：「踐踏法治 警暴濫權 以謊言和子彈治港」。團隊是次邀請到4位市民，分別有運動中擔任救護員身份、普通家庭主婦、集會工作人員等，上來分享相關經驗。團隊希望能借是次機會，提供多角度意見，還原事真言，從而反駁警方及政府過去的謊言。<br />\n<br />\n現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年8月8日<br />\n時間：14：00<br />\n<br />\n記者會後將設有問答環節，由於會場座位有限，有興趣進場採訪的媒體請於 8月 7日（星期三）晚上11點30分或之前回覆，以便安排。<br />\n<br />\n如有查詢，請聯絡金先生 （電話：94377274）。謝謝<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n採訪主任、編輯及記者<br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n2019 年 8 月 7 日"},{"pid":"1815496bda87c63168e6a0f3e1b04aa5f93aba89","tid":1429981,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bb8bc3f0cab2d75f4c169af8f246862ddec49e","tid":1429981,"uid":294966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:09:46.000Z","msg":"發現自己開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35720ec143fa7c74d91ead55f66b80d9ad8b5a8d","tid":1429981,"uid":294966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7bb8bc3f0cab2d75f4c169af8f246862ddec49e","tid":1429981,"uid":294966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:09:46.000Z","msg":"發現自己開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"新post:"},{"pid":"944e3b0b9dc6cc09e4e03600af0242b023ada439","tid":1429981,"uid":268725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"Btw, 我會接機！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家集中火力推8月9-11